# Prettier ignore file
# Installed to .prettierignore by make install-repo
#
# Pre-commit passes explicit file paths to prettier, bypassing .prettierignore
# in normal operation. The exclude: pattern in .pre-commit-config.yaml is the
# authoritative way to exclude files from the prettier pre-commit hook.
# This file handles direct prettier invocations (e.g. editor integrations).

# Claude Code plugin skill and constitution files — contain template syntax
# that prettier rewrites and destroys (e.g. {{VARIABLE}}, fenced YAML blocks)
SKILL.md
CONSTITUTION.md
